We enjoyed cocktails in the lounge but didn't get to try the restaurant, although the menu was impressive, as we were going elsewhere for dinner.	The restaurant food and service was so good, it was almost a disappoint when we ate anywhere else in Seattle.	Every detail is covered.....we ate at ART for breakfast and dinner and the food was very good.	We had drinks and snacks one evening in the ART bar, which was positively buzzing (it WAS Happy Hour) with a most convivial atmosphere.